name: CLUBHATSCLUB #3
description:
5 COLLECTIBLE CARDS WITH THE INSIGNIA CHARACTER FROM CLUBHATSCLUB! 
this time we got 5 static cards with the character of clubhatsclub they are made in collaboration with 87Geve A.K.A Laquenosetranca! a great artist and illustrator from Corrientes, ARG in charge of the unification of worlds between music and collectible cards!

The Gang is looking for human allies. Owning a CLUBHATS NFT is your access to the ClubHats Club!, a world of unparalleled energy, power and the unknown. But you must act quickly if you want to achieve self-mastery.
